{"id": 1789, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都会因为什么原因回购？", "description": "听过那么多“欢迎再来”，在买东西这事上， 你到底是为啥成为回头客的？欢迎补充！（题图：Giphy)", "record_count": 11946, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170707153451ecbWQdD0n1XYROvi.gif", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-16T17:00:35Z", "questions": [{"id": 2581, "title": "现如今你都会因为什么原因回购？", "content": "如今你都会因为什么原因回购", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 219808, "content": "假货太多，好不容易逮着靠谱代购要珍惜", "image": "img/option/option/20170706234031geS8GNmW2Punl3hA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219809, "content": "品牌铁粉，认准苹果、可口可乐…", "image": "img/option/option/20170706234214DShZVnUJPbYCmLz7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219810, "content": "有会员积分返利的，没啥大毛病就盯着他家买了，还能打折", "image": "img/option/option/20170706234413bAnR9oPtXhUy5dBa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219811, "content": "正在用的东西打折或是要停产了，囤货", "image": "img/option/option/20170709121819be7zRENIMkDLcQim.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219812, "content": "真·爱用品，还要发自肺腑安利别人那种", "image": "img/option/option/20170706234953tpHy5NMFJBV3qPQ9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219813, "content": "爱豆代言的东西要一直捧场", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235236E8b36JB2lKcD0jzT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219814, "content": "怀旧，好的就是这口小时候的味道", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235548v473KmjirzHoLc1t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219815, "content": "商家给了抵用券，一直找机会要用掉的", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235603cy3oTAiN02nU5I8Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219816, "content": "为了发条“万年回购”的朋友圈，显摆一下我都买了啥", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235519mDHkMLXNnZ0BOU6i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219817, "content": "喜欢的设计师品牌，每季总要买一件", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235633WXwlzKIGNBYbUS17.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219818, "content": "懒得看测评功课，习惯性回购，省事", "image": "img/option/option/20170706235706zagV8IR2HwY5jXEd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220155, "content": "常年买的店购物体验好，店员会适时出现，不盯人", "image": "img/option/option/20170709131113p4gPeWrZj7FMDNAY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}